original_title: Sean Dorsey Dance: Dreaming Trans and Queer Futures
overview: This profile of trailblazing transgender choreographer and activist Sean Dorsey features powerful dance sequences to reinforce the fact that trans, gender-nonconforming, and queer people are strong, wise, powerful, beautiful, and visionary artists and leaders.
title: Sean Dorsey Dance: Dreaming Trans and Queer Futures
